---
/**
 * Mission statement: testo grande a sinistra, orb a gradiente a destra
 * (come la fascia "We help enterprises reimagine..." del riferimento).
 */
---

<section class="mission section" aria-label="La nostra missione">
  <div class="container mission__grid">
    <p class="mission__text" data-reveal="blur">
      Aiutiamo le imprese del territorio a crescere con siti web, e-commerce,
      SEO e software su misura. <strong>Un unico partner</strong> per tutta la
      tua presenza digitale: dalla strategia al codice, dal lancio ai risultati.
    </p>
    <div class="mission__orb orb" aria-hidden="true" data-reveal="scale"></div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .mission__grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1.5fr) minmax(0, 1fr);
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--sp-7);
  }
  .mission__text {
    font-family: var(--font-heading);
    font-size: var(--fs-xl);
    font-weight: var(--fw-medium);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    line-height: var(--lh-snug);
    color: var(--c-text);
    text-wrap: balance;
  }
  .mission__text strong { color: var(--c-text); }
  .mission__orb {
    width: min(100%, 320px);
    aspect-ratio: 1;
    justify-self: center;
  }
  @media (max-width: 820px) {
    .mission__grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }
    .mission__orb { width: 200px; }
  }
</style>
